OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few shallow mist and fog
OL,6,Fpatches possible around dawn soon
OL,7,Fclearing. Otherwise another dry day
OL,8,Fwith plenty of sunshine. Very warm or
OL,9,Fhot. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA fine end to the day and
OL,12,Fstaying dry and mainly clear
OL,13,Fovernight. Some low cloud possibly
OL,14,Fforming around the North Coast.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FAny low cloud soon clearing
OL,17,Fduring the morning with bright and
OL,18,Fsunny spells. Temperatures down a bit,
OL,19,Fbut still warm or very warm in any
OL,20,Fsunshine. Light northwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
