OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and settled. Cloudy or bright with
OL,7,Fsunny spells developing. Feeling warm
OL,8,Fin any sunshine. Light or moderate
OL,9,Fnorthwest winds.
